<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4538616>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 8. — Stichoporina reussi Stoliczka, 1862; A, lectotype colony; B, colony margin showing budding pattern; C, a smaller syntype colony; D, detail of ooecium; E, abfrontal view of colony showing a single pore in zooecial basal wall; F, transverse section of colony showing arrangement of autozooecia in one row with a highly calcified central part; G, section showing internal view of autozooecia. Scale bars: 100 μm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4538616/files/figure.png" .

